
'''= an overview of how the internet has disintermediated traditional media production and distribution businesses'''


* Source: [http://www.cato.org/pub_display.php?pub_id=6359 Policy Report: Amateur-to-Amateur: The Rise of a New Creative Culture]. by F. Gregory Lastowka and Dan Hunter. Cato Institute, April 2006

